OL,3,CRace attacks soar in 'year of hate'
OL,5,FA new report has shown the highest
OL,6,Flevels of racist incidents and crimes
OL,7,Fin Northern Ireland since records
OL,8,Fbegan.
OL,10,FRecords started in 2004 with the
OL,11,Flevels of race hate incidents hitting
OL,12,Fa new high in summer 2024.
OL,14,FAmnesty International described the
OL,15,Fpast year as a 'year of hate'.
OL,17,FThe figures - up to March 2025 - were
OL,18,Fpublished in a report by the PSNI and
OL,19,Fthe Northern Ireland Statistics and
OL,20,FResearch Agency.
