OL,3,CRace attacks soar in 'year of hate'
OL,5,FIt reveals there were 1,807 incidents
OL,6,Fand 1,188 crimes recorded by the
OL,7,Fpolice.
OL,9,FThere were 454 more race incidents and
OL,10,F349 more race hate crimes recorded in
OL,11,Fthe last 12 months than in the
OL,12,Fprevious corresponding period.
OL,14,FSix of the eight highest monthly
OL,15,Flevels of race incidents since records
OL,16,Fbegan were recorded between May and
OL,17,FOctober 2024.
OL,19,FMore than half (635) of recorded race
OL,20,Fhate crimes in the period were in
OL,21,FBelfast.
