OL,3,CRace attacks soar in 'year of hate'
OL,5,FPatrick Corrigan, Amnesty
OL,6,FInternational's Northern Ireland
OL,7,FDirector, said: "The past year has
OL,8,Fbeen a year of hate for victims of
OL,9,Fracism in Northern Ireland. These
OL,10,Ffigures should serve as a stark wake-
OL,11,Fup call for the Northern Ireland
OL,12,FExecutive.
OL,14,F"The Executive's ten-year racial
OL,15,Fequality strategy has failed. Promises
OL,16,Fmade years ago remain broken, while
OL,17,Fracism has been allowed to flourish.
OL,18,FLast year, race hate crime hit an all-
OL,19,Ftime high ` a shameful milestone," he
OL,20,Fadded.
