OL,3,CRace attacks soar in 'year of hate'
OL,5,F"As the current Racial Equality
OL,6,FStrategy nears its expiration at the
OL,7,Fend of this year, the Executive must
OL,8,Fdeliver more than rhetoric. It must
OL,9,Fimplement a bold, effective action
OL,10,Fplan to confront and dismantle the
OL,11,Ftoxic prejudice that has taken root
OL,12,Facross Northern Ireland."
OL,14,FAn independent review of the Northern
OL,15,FIreland Executive's Racial Equality
OL,16,FStrategy 2015 - 2025, commissioned by
OL,17,Fthe Executive and published in
OL,18,FDecember 2024, found the strategy has
OL,19,Fbeen undermined by the lack of an
OL,20,Faction plan and budget.
